\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \emptyset,\left\{ a\right\} ,\left\{ b\right\} \right\} $
\end_inset

.
 In figura 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Argomento-a-difeso"

\end_inset

